snippet.title: 13Z - Official Global Playtest Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Enjoy this new gameplay trailer for 13Z, an upcoming action-heavy fantasy-themed hack-'n'-slash third-person roguelike. The global playtest launches on Steam tomorrow, September 19. Check it out on Steam if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2348250/13Z/

#IGN #Gaming
